00:00:13.540 --> 00:00:15.540
Today , we are making "Noodles with Peanut Sauce".

00:00:38.686 --> 00:00:40.686
For the peanut sauce, boil 1/2 cup of water in a small pan.

00:00:44.881 --> 00:00:46.881
Add the jaggery.

00:00:52.446 --> 00:00:54.446
Add the peanut butter.

00:00:59.154 --> 00:01:01.154
Add the tamarind pulp.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Add salt to taste.

00:01:10.615 --> 00:01:12.615
Mix well and simmer for a few minutes or 
 till the jaggery melts and the sauce thickens.

00:01:40.810 --> 00:01:42.810
Add the soya sauce.

00:01:58.086 --> 00:02:00.090
For the noodles, heat the oil in a broad non-stick pan.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.000
Add the spring onion whites and sauté on a high flame for 
 2 to 3 minutes or till the onions turn translucent.

00:02:27.731 --> 00:02:29.730
Add the shredded purple cabbage.

00:02:30.707 --> 00:02:32.710
Add the bean sprouts.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:38.000
Add the carrots.

00:02:39.558 --> 00:02:41.560
Add the cottage cheese cubes.

00:02:41.700 --> 00:02:43.700
Sauté on a high flame for 2 to 3 minutes.

00:02:48.214 --> 00:02:50.210
Add the boiled flat rice noodles.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:55.000
Add salt to taste.

00:02:56.793 --> 00:02:58.790
Mix well and cook on a high flame for 
 2 to 3 minutes, while stirring occasionally.

00:03:12.834 --> 00:03:14.830
Add the prepared peanut sauce.

00:03:20.705 --> 00:03:22.700
Mix well.

00:03:26.347 --> 00:03:28.350
Add freshly ground pepper to taste.

00:03:29.427 --> 00:03:31.430
Serve immediately garnished with spring onion greens.

